high_descs: Walk over to face the coffee table.
Pick up the credit card to the left of the lap top.
Walk over to the open box on the coffee table.
Put the credit card inside of the box.
Pick up the box from the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the brown shelf.
Put the box down on the right side of the shelf.
anns.task_desc: To put a credit card inside a box and move the box to the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, proceed to center of coffee table on right, turn right to face coffee table.
Pick up credit card from table, directly left of tea pot.
Turn right, go to end of coffee table.  Turn left then left to face end of coffee table.
Place credit card in box on coffee table.
Pick up box and credit card from coffee table.
Turn left, proceed to shelf against wall.
Place box on right side of shelf, to the right of the newspapers.
anns.task_desc: Move credit card from table to coffee table, place it in a box, pick up box with credit card, move both to shelf.

high_descs: Walk left and forward up to the coffee table
Pick up the blue credit card from the table
Turn right and walk around to face the right side of the coffee table
Put the credit card in the cardboard box on the coffee table
Pick up the cardboard box from the table
Turn left and walk forward to the dark bench
Put the box down on the dark bench
anns.task_desc: Put the cardboard box with credit card on the dark bench
